{"TopicId":187274,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;Rear-view\u0026quot; Camera?","CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-17T23:58:10Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"StrandedonEarth","CreatedById":89439,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-17T23:58:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow hard would it be to assign a button that, while pressed, instantly shows a a view that is 180 degrees from the current view, still aimed at the current aim point (as in the viewpoint would have to move to the other side of the craft)? Similar to the rear-view button in car racing games...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, it may not get a lot of use, but it could be useful at times...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-18T06:21:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223652184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566086290\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, it may not get a lot of use\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cem\u003EDreamchaser\u003C/em\u003E bless you.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Martian Emigrant","CreatedById":158362,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-18T12:57:00Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223652184\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022187274\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221566086290\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002289439\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022StrandedonEarth\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 hours ago, StrandedonEarth said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHow hard would it be to assign a button that, while pressed, instantly shows a a view that is 180 degrees from the current view, still aimed at the current aim point (as in the viewpoint would have to move to the other side of the craft)? Similar to the rear-view button in car racing games...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, it may not get a lot of use, but it could be useful at times...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI like that.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOne of my bane is looking at a ship and doing an EVA. The Kerbal is always on the other side and the whole camera as to be rotated. Grump.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYour magic button would be used by one such as me.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nME\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"kerbiloid","CreatedById":129408,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-08-19T05:33:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr a mini-window with this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler\u0022 data-ipsspoiler=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_header\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ESpoiler\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsSpoiler_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00227145899-photo-shot-of-car-rearview-mirro\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 data-ratio=\u002266.62\u0022 height=\u0022682\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022 src=\u0022https://previews.123rf.com/images/jirkaejc/jirkaejc1006/jirkaejc100600002/7145899-photo-shot-of-car-r